<plot>An unhappy butcher, kvetching as he swings his cleaver at a side of meat, cuts off several rib steaks and lets them fall to the floor. He kicks them around and continues his butchering. Then, by accident, he hacks off a thumb and that's only the beginning of the wounds of outrageous fortune. He keeps up his complaining to the bitter end.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?347636</url></doc>
